channel.title: I can log in with ham and no-ip on MY computer
channel.description: Hi, I have a server called Chazscape Pkz :D But.... Ham works fine. But when it comes to no-ip things get bad. I have a no-ip. Its Called...Chaz.no-ip.biz, I can get on it But on my threads i get things like.. "Omfg I cant use no-ip!! :mad: :mad:" Or "Z0mg Why cant i log in! turn no-ip on!!!" Well i need to sort that out my hame works fine. But i can get on my no-ip but other poeple cant.. Tell me whats wrong please?? Also it wont add to the server status page either. I will be happy if somone could tell me how to put it on?
